  "2274340": {
    "name": "Colossal Cave VR",
    "steam_appid": 2274340,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/d4129a330c783040f8b838b95cb174fe.poster.avif?t=1770413662\" width=616 height=44 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/d4129a330c783040f8b838b95cb174fe.webm?t=1770413662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/d4129a330c783040f8b838b95cb174fe.mp4?t=1770413662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>踏上一段穿越时空的冒险旅程，探索一个广袤的洞穴系统，这里充满了宝藏、奇异生物、迷宫和让人绞尽脑汁的谜题。这款冒险游戏的始祖将考验你的逻辑思维与问题解决能力，伴你一步步揭开它的故事与秘密。通过不断的尝试与探索，你将穿越狭窄通道、进入令人惊叹的洞窟、收集物品、寻找宝藏、击退小矮人的袭击——在灯光熄灭之前，记得盯紧你的得分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还记得你七八十年代的《Colossal Cave》老地图吗？拿出来照样好用！这是一款忠于原作、毫无改动的致敬之作。需要点提示？卡在龙那里了吗？拨打我们的<i>经典提示热线</i>：<strong>1-206-207-9017</strong> 获取帮助。卡关了吗？试着在网上查找几十年来的通关技巧——原版中的所有策略在这里依然有效！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/50147464c9a4090114b8af097ad269f3.poster.avif?t=1770413662\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/50147464c9a4090114b8af097ad269f3.webm?t=1770413662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/50147464c9a4090114b8af097ad269f3.mp4?t=1770413662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/b83469709ab75674435de739eac139b5.poster.avif?t=1770413662\" width=616 height=42 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/b83469709ab75674435de739eac139b5.webm?t=1770413662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/b83469709ab75674435de739eac139b5.mp4?t=1770413662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>本作最初由一位业余洞穴探险者在20世纪70年代中期开发，起初只是为了让他的两个女儿开心。Will Crowther 的灵感来自他与妻子 Patricia 共同绘制的肯塔基州猛犸洞穴中 Bedquilt 区域的详尽地图。家庭探洞之旅正是这款游戏的灵魂所在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随后，编程爱好者 Don Woods 在 ARPANET 网络上发现了这款游戏，并对其进行了大幅扩展，加入了更多的幻想元素、谜题内容以及一个复杂的 350 分系统。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多年后，Don 的扩展版本成为了最广为流传、最具代表性的<i>Colossal Cave Adventure</i>版本。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/9d8b4c39ed4307fe114478d4749f07e2.poster.avif?t=1770413662\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/9d8b4c39ed4307fe114478d4749f07e2.webm?t=1770413662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/9d8b4c39ed4307fe114478d4749f07e2.mp4?t=1770413662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/c0ccc5da935d8627ea1b15b2a2eeaa74.poster.avif?t=1770413662\" width=616 height=42 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/c0ccc5da935d8627ea1b15b2a2eeaa74.webm?t=1770413662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/c0ccc5da935d8627ea1b15b2a2eeaa74.mp4?t=1770413662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>1979 年，Roberta Williams 第一次接触这款游戏，立刻被深深吸引。她连续几周沉浸其中，一边做笔记，一边根据文本描述绘制洞穴地图。她的脑海中充满了荧光蘑菇、迷雾缭绕的地下湖、易怒的双壳软体动物，以及一个神秘消失的巨人。在完成 350 分并通关之后，她渴望继续冒险——但在 1979 年，如果你想要新的冒险，那就只能自己动手做！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >于是她真的做到了。1980 年，Roberta 创作并发布了世界上第一款图形冒险游戏：<i>Mystery House</i>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/c029eaacdc8401ecf23f1c42e34e2f45.poster.avif?t=1770413662\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/c029eaacdc8401ecf23f1c42e34e2f45.webm?t=1770413662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/c029eaacdc8401ecf23f1c42e34e2f45.mp4?t=1770413662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/3b9f76f24de09bac60406b83dc273fbf.poster.avif?t=1770413662\" width=616 height=44 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/3b9f76f24de09bac60406b83dc273fbf.webm?t=1770413662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/3b9f76f24de09bac60406b83dc273fbf.mp4?t=1770413662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>这款具有里程碑意义的游戏被认为是史上最具影响力的作品之一，它奠定了冒险类游戏的诸多基本标准。它几乎被移植到了所有电脑与主机平台，被数百万玩家游玩，并启发了无数游戏、图书、影视作品的创作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重温冒险游戏的黄金时代。沉浸于一个充满宝藏、奇幻生物与高智商谜题的庞大洞穴系统中。回到那个更纯粹的年代，感受 point-and-click 操作的复古魅力，以及致敬经典的艺术风格。这款满载敬意的重制版本由精品独立游戏工作室 Cygnus Entertainment 倾力打造。Ken 和 Roberta Williams 坚信并致力于传承经典冒险游戏的精神。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/7ce862ba1ba2bf5e9e7a9297105b430d.poster.avif?t=1770413662\" width=616 height=42 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/7ce862ba1ba2bf5e9e7a9297105b430d.webm?t=1770413662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/7ce862ba1ba2bf5e9e7a9297105b430d.mp4?t=1770413662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>这款 VR 探索类游戏拥有大量巧妙又富挑战性的谜题，将让你爱不释手。探索 14 个独具特色的区域，那里有魔法、隐藏的秘密、令人惊叹的景观和各类洞穴生物。每一处都提供独特而迷人的冒险体验。加上超过 20 项可解锁的成就，让你沉浸数小时！</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >简单直观的 point-and-click 操作方式  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸式、色彩丰富且极具吸引力的区域  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >富有逻辑挑战性的谜题设计  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战与奖励之间的绝妙平衡  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隐藏秘密的地下奇景  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 多项独立成就可解锁  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >令人愉悦且引人入胜的游戏体验  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >前所未有的探索冒险  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/0a1cba2adf08247713fad71590c0d2ae.poster.avif?t=1770413662\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/0a1cba2adf08247713fad71590c0d2ae.webm?t=1770413662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/0a1cba2adf08247713fad71590c0d2ae.mp4?t=1770413662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/9d82e1a926e8c0164e83fe989a62f6a2.poster.avif?t=1770413662\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/9d82e1a926e8c0164e83fe989a62f6a2.webm?t=1770413662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274340/extras/9d82e1a926e8c0164e83fe989a62f6a2.mp4?t=1770413662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏虽源自经典，却并非只是情怀，它历经时间考验，至今仍被广大玩家喜爱——因为它真的很好玩！它既有趣又富有深度，既简单又复杂，极具创意——正如 Roberta 所说：“这是一次精彩的设计。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快进入 <i>Colossal Cave</i> 的深处开始冒险吧。别忘了带上你的灯！</p>",
